properties.Name: BC1
properties.Flora: Blue pine and  dry alpine acrees
properties.Fauna: Snow leopard, Tigers, White-lipped deer, birds and butterfly species
properties.Descriptio: It connects Jigme Dorji National Park and jigme Khesar Strict Nature Reserve

properties.Name: BC2
properties.Flora: Rhododendrons, blue poppy, Primula and Gentiana
properties.Fauna: Royal Bengal Tiger, Asiatic Wild dog, Himalayan Red Panda, Blyth's tragopan, Satyr tragopan, wild asian cat,
properties.Descriptio: It connects Jigme Dorji National Park and Jigme singye Wangchuck National Park

properties.Name: BC3
properties.Fauna: Barking Deer, Guar, Himilayan goral, Sambar,Clouded Leopard, Marbled Cat, Tiger, Dhole(Wild dog), Orange bellied Himalayan Squirrel,Rhesus macaque and Masked palm civet
properties.Descriptio: It connects Jigme Singye Wangchuck National Park, Royal Manas National Park in the northeast to Phibsoo Wildlife Sanctuary in the southeast.

properties.Name: BC4
properties.Flora: Herbs: (Begonia flaviflora hara, Begonia gemmipara, Impatiens sikkimensis,Begonia bhutanensis and impatiens pseudolavigata), Orchid: (Panisea panchaseensis, plathanthera dunglonggenisis and bulbophyllum andersonii)
properties.Fauna: White Bellied Heron, Steppe Eagle, Rufous-necked hornbill, Grey-crowned, Mountain Hawk Eagle, Himalayan Griffon, Yellow-rumped Honeyguide, Satyr Tragopan, Ward's, Prinia and Beautiful Nuthatch
properties.Descriptio: It connects Royal Manas National Park in the south, Thrumshingla National Park in the North and Jigme Singye Wangchuck National Park in the west

properties.Name: BC5
properties.Flora: Lantana camara, Chromolaena odoratum, Micaniamicrantha, Ageratina adeniphora and Ageratum adenophora
properties.Fauna: Barking deer, Wild Pig, Indian crestless Porcupine, Asian Elephant,Guar, Wild Boar and sambar
properties.Descriptio: It connects Royal Manas Park and Jomotshangkha Wildlife Sanctuary

properties.Name: BC6
properties.Flora: Blue poppy, Rhododendron, Primula, Gentiana and cordyceps
properties.Fauna: Roysl Bengal tiger, Asiatic Wild Dog, Snow leopard, Himalayan red fox, barking deer, Assamese macaw, Blood Pheasant and grey-backed shrike
properties.Descriptio: It connects Jomotshangkha Wildlife Sanctuary and Sakteng Wildlife Sanctuary

properties.Name: BC7
properties.Fauna: Snow Leopard, Royal Bengal Tiger, Red panda and Balck necked Crane
properties.Descriptio: It connects Bumdeling Wildlife Sanctuary, Thrumshingla National Park in the south-west and Wangchuck Centennial National Park in the north-west

properties.Name: BC8
properties.Flora: Prunus, Betula alnoides,Acer species, Juglans regia, Sorbus insignia, Rhododendrons species, Symplocas species, Quercus Lamellosa and Lynia ovaliafolia
properties.Fauna: Asiatic Golden Cat, clouded leopard, tiger, leopard cat, marbled cat, wild dog, red fox, black bear, deer, sambar, yak, Himalayan musk deer, wild pig and Indian Porcupine
properties.Descriptio: It connects Jigme Dorji National Park in the north, Wangchuck Centennial National Park in the north and Jigme Singye Wangchuck National Park in the south
